reviewText: Big fan of the Universal Century Gundam series, and Unicorn Gundam delivered on all levels.  Great conclusion to a great series.
Great end to the series with fantastic visuals.

Product was the Japanese version but since it was a multiple language release and was compatible with all regions. The blue ray played in English perfectly. The animation is great and for any mecha/gundam enthusiast Unicorn is a great addition. This final volume raps everything up from the series.
